{"tid":1863571,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"東亞銀行 36樓有兩人接觸過武漢肺炎病人","createTime":"2020-02-05T08:13:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T08:17:44.000Z","uid":152123,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d6fc08e03726127e4edc564a42b6b1f280387e6a","tid":1863571,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T08:13:37.000Z","msg":"各位同事注意：<br />\n<br />\n我們剛獲悉，有兩名同於東亞銀行中心36樓工作的同事，於剛過去的周日曾與一名新型冠狀病毒的確診者有接觸。本行在接報後已即時安排該等同事的工作樓層（包括洗手間和茶水間）丶職員餐廳及電梯進行徹底清潔和消毒。有關同事目前未有感染徴狀，惟為安全起見，本行已安排他們及與其有緊密接觸的同事自我隔離。<br />\n<br />\n本行一向重視員工的健康和安全，亦鼓勵所有員工如感到不適，應該留家休息。<br />\n<br />\nInternal message of BEA<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（另外，25樓都疑似有人中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"d720a0e47fea0637f2ac3249a16bf97312c0e043","tid":1863571,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T08:14:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc27c17b6abfde5657a004182eb62ce12163ca13","tid":1863571,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d720a0e47fea0637f2ac3249a16bf97312c0e043","tid":1863571,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T08:14:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T08:15:14.000Z","msg":"牙佬，要再見了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2104469f2bd74f2b477d30668f070d54e5f977ca","tid":1863571,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc27c17b6abfde5657a004182eb62ce12163ca13","tid":1863571,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d720a0e47fea0637f2ac3249a16bf97312c0e043","tid":1863571,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T08:14:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T08:15:14.000Z","msg":"牙佬，要再見了<img src=\"/asse